    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i am looking at my student loan statement and the math isnt making sense. i make my payments every month on time but the principal amount is barely moving. why does it feel like the balance stays almost the same even though i am paying money every month?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
